---
title: Montreal-Spiced Bacon-Wrapped Steak with Garlic Beans and Creamy Mash
description: Bacon-wrapped steak, need I say more? This pan-seared steak gets the royal treatment with salty, crispy bacon and a rich pan sauce. Creamy mash and garlicky green beans round out this winning weeknight dish.
